    {
      "id": "step1_welcome",
      "title": "欢迎使用 Pulsar！",
      "description": "Pulsar 是一个基于肌肉记忆的快速启动器。让我们用 2 分钟了解核心功能：\n\n• 两种触发模式：\n  - 任务模式 (Ctrl+Q)：快速切换窗口\n  - 动作模式 (Ctrl+Shift+Q)：执行应用专属命令\n\n• 空间定位，盲操作友好",
      "type": "Instruction",
      "target": null,
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "ButtonClick",
        "targetValue": "StartButton"
      },
      "layout": {
        "cardPosition": "TopRight",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 450,
        "fixedCardHeight": 300
      },
      "focusMode": "AlwaysObserving"
    },
    {
      "id": "step2_open_settings",
      "title": "打开设置界面",
      "description": "点击下方按钮打开设置界面\n\n💡 提示：你也可以通过托盘图标打开设置",
      "type": "Instruction",
      "target": null,
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "WindowOpened",
        "targetValue": "SettingsWindow"
