    {
      "id": "step3_settings_overview",
      "title": "设置界面导览",
      "description": "这里可以配置 Pulsar 的所有功能：\n\n• 常规 - 热键、主题、启动项\n• 槽位配置 - 为不同应用配置快捷操作\n• 插件 - 管理功能扩展\n\n每个 Profile 可配置不同的槽位：\n• 通过顶部下拉框切换 Profile\n• 每个 Profile 的槽位独立配置",
      "type": "Instruction",
      "target": {
        "type": "Window",
        "elementName": "SettingsWindow"
      },
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "ButtonClick",
        "targetValue": "NextButton"
      },
      "layout": {
        "targetWindow": {
          "left": 0.25,
          "top": 0.15,
          "width": 0.5,
          "height": 0.7,
          "isRelative": true
        },
        "cardPosition": "TopRight",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 450,
        "fixedCardHeight": 300
      },
      "focusMode": "AlwaysObserving"
    },
    {
      "id": "step4_navigate_slots",
      "title": "进入槽位配置",
      "description": "请点击左侧导航栏的\"槽位配置\"\n\n槽位配置是 Pulsar 的核心功能：\n• 为不同应用配置专属快捷操作\n• 通过顶部下拉框选择要配置的 Profile\n• Global Profile 的槽位在所有应用中可用",
      "type": "WaitForNavigation",
      "target": {
        "type": "UIElement",
        "elementName": "SlotsNavigationItem"
      },
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "NavigationItemClicked",
