      "layout": {
        "targetWindow": {
          "left": 0.25,
          "top": 0.15,
          "width": 0.5,
          "height": 0.7,
          "isRelative": true
        },
        "cardPosition": "TopRight",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 450,
        "fixedCardHeight": 300
      },
      "focusMode": "AlwaysObserving"
    },
    {
      "id": "step5_add_winswitcher_slot",
      "title": "配置窗口切换槽位",
      "description": "让我们添加一个窗口切换槽位\n\n步骤：\n1. 在顶部下拉框中选择 \"Launcher\" Context\n   （这会显示 Global Profile 的 SwitchMode 槽位）\n2. 点击底部的 [Add Slot] 按钮\n3. 在弹出菜单中选择 \"Window Switcher\" 插件\n4. 在 app 参数中输入：notepad\n5. 在 Display Label 中输入：记事本\n6. 点击卡片外部区域收起配置\n\n💡 提示：这个槽位会在任务模式 (Ctrl+Q) 时显示",
      "type": "WaitForAction",
      "target": {
        "type": "UIElement",
        "elementName": "AddSlotButton"
      },
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "SlotAdded",
        "targetValue": "{\"PluginId\":\"com.pulsar.winswitcher\",\"Profile\":\"Global\"}"
      },
      "layout": {
        "targetWindow": {
          "left": 0.25,
          "top": 0.15,
          "width": 0.5,
          "height": 0.7,
          "isRelative": true
        },
        "cardPosition": "TopRight",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 450,
        "fixedCardHeight": 350
      },
      "focusMode": "AlwaysObserving"
    },
    {
      "id": "step6_test_switch_mode",
      "title": "测试任务模式",
      "description": "现在让我们测试任务模式的窗口切换功能！\n\n步骤：\n1. 按下 Ctrl+Q 触发任务模式\n2. 移动鼠标到 \"记事本\" 槽位\n3. 释放按键，Pulsar 会打开/切换到记事本\n\n💡 提示：\n• 任务模式 (Ctrl+Q) 用于快速切换窗口\n• 外圈显示静态配置的应用\n• 中心显示最近使用 (MRU) 的窗口",
      "type": "WaitForAction",
      "target": null,
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "RadialMenuShown",
        "targetValue": "Task"
      },
      "layout": {
        "cardPosition": "TopRight",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 450,
        "fixedCardHeight": 300
      },
      "focusMode": "AlwaysObserving"
    },
    {
      "id": "step7_add_command_slot",
      "title": "配置应用专属命令槽位",
      "description": "现在记事本已经打开，让我们为它配置专属命令槽位\n\n步骤：\n1. 回到设置窗口\n2. 在顶部下拉框中选择 \"Notepad\" Profile\n3. 点击底部的 [Add Slot] 按钮\n4. 选择任意插件并配置参数\n5. 设置 Display Label\n6. 点击卡片外部区域收起配置\n\n💡 提示：这个槽位会在动作模式 (Ctrl+Shift+Q) 激活记事本时显示",
      "type": "WaitForAction",
      "target": {
        "type": "UIElement",
        "elementName": "NotepadProfile"
      },
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "SlotAdded",
        "targetValue": "{\"Profile\":\"notepad\"}"
      },
      "layout": {
        "targetWindow": {
          "left": 0.05,
          "top": 0.1,
          "width": 0.5,
          "height": 0.8,
          "isRelative": true
        },
        "externalWindows": {
          "notepad": {
            "left": 0.57,
            "top": 0.1,
            "width": 0.38,
            "height": 0.8,
            "isRelative": true
          }
        },
        "cardPosition": "TopRight",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 450,
        "fixedCardHeight": 380
      },
      "focusMode": "AlwaysObserving"
    },
    {
      "id": "step8_test_command_mode",
      "title": "测试动作模式",
      "description": "最后一步！让我们测试动作模式\n\n步骤：\n1. 确保记事本窗口处于激活状态\n2. 按下 Ctrl+Shift+Q 触发动作模式\n3. 移动鼠标到配置的槽位\n4. 释放按键，执行对应操作\n\n💡 提示：动作模式 (Ctrl+Shift+Q) 会根据当前激活的应用显示专属命令",
      "type": "WaitForAction",
      "target": null,
      "completionTrigger": {
        "type": "RadialMenuShown",
        "targetValue": "Action"
      },
      "layout": {
        "cardPosition": "TopRight",
        "cardSizeMode": "Fixed",
        "fixedCardWidth": 450,
        "fixedCardHeight": 300
      },
      "focusMode": "AlwaysObserving"
    },
    {
      "id": "step9_completion",
      "title": "恭喜！教程完成",
      "description": "你已经掌握了 Pulsar 的核心功能：\n\n✅ 任务模式 (Ctrl+Q)\n   快速切换窗口，外圈静态配置 + 中心 MRU\n\n✅ 动作模式 (Ctrl+Shift+Q)\n   执行当前应用的专属命令\n\n✅ Profile 配置\n   每个应用可配置独立的槽位\n   Global Profile 在所有应用中可用\n\n💡 提示：\n• 在设置中可以随时重新查看教程\n• 支持为每个应用配置专属操作\n• 更多插件请访问插件市场",
      "type": "Instruction",
